<HL>
   X-Rite Inc. Unveils Product
</HL>
<DATE>
05/18/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   XRIT
</CO>
<LP>
   GRANDVILLE, Mich. -- X-Rite Inc. introduced an instrument
used for measuring shades of color in the graphic arts
industry.
   Production of the so-called X-scanning densitometer is
expected during the fourth quarter of 1990, the company said.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   In addition, X-Rite said it is adding 30,000 square feet
of specialized production area to its existing facility to
cover an expected increase in sales of instruments.
</TEXT>
